lead_paragraph: Jefferson Mena and David Villa scored a minute apart before the game was 10 minutes old and New York City FC clinched a playoff berth with a 4-1 victory over the Chicago Fire on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Quick Start, Villa's 2 Goals Puts NYCFC in Playoffs
